programme.title: World Watch: Africa’s Hunter Ep18
programme.desc: Ikuti kehidupan pemangsa hebat di Zambia seperti singa, harimau bintang dan hyena, yang bersaing dalam dunia liar yang semakin mencabar. Pelbagai perubahan berlaku dari kelahiran impala serentak hingga kemunculan makhluk ganjil seperti anai-anai terbang. Alam liar Lembah ini bersedia menghadapi musim baharu. Episod kali ini mengenai konfrontasi luar biasa berlaku antara dua lawan yang tidak mungkin dan setanding,singa dan tiga ratus kumpulan kerbau yang kuat di Lembah Luangwa di Zambia.

programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. programme.title: Simfoni Alam
programme.desc: Dokumentari memaparkan isu hidupan liar dan alam semulajadi. Taman Negara di Jerantut Pahang, merupakan destinasi menarik yang menjadi tarikan pelancong domestik dan antarabangsa menerusi bidang eko pelancongan berasaskan alam sekitar dan budaya tempatan. Juga, usaha Jabatan Perhilitan dalam memastikan Taman Negara terus dipelihara dari sebarang kerosakan agar ianya dapat terus dinikmati oleh generasi akan datang.

programme.title: Galaksi Ep7
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Setiap episod mengandungi 3 segmen iaitu Tajuk Utama, Tahukah Anda (membawa trivia dan fakta menarik) dan Eksperimen (yang boleh dilakukan di rumah). Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim membawa penonton meneroka fenomena Kerdipan Bintang, mengenali objek-objek langit yang memancarkan cahaya dan terdiri daripada nebula, serta memahami pengkelasan bintang. Dalam segmen Tahukah Anda, penonton akan mengetahui bahawa Malaysia telah diberi penghormatan untuk menamakan sebuah bintang. Segmen Eksperimen pula mengajar cara membina Rajah HR untuk memahami klasifikasi bintang dengan lebih jelas.

programme.title: Spektra: Derhaka Cinta Jebat Ep25
programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. Bijaknya Jebat mengatur rancangan agar Aisyah jatuh cinta padanya hingga membawa kepada sebuah perkahwinan dengan niat ingin membalas dendam. Aisyah Humaira, suatu ketika dahulu pernah menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan adik lelaki Jebat, iaitu Tuah Iskandar. Tanpa usul periksa Jebat menjatuhkan hukuman tanpa memberi peluang kepada Aisyah untuk menjelaskan segala-galanya. Aisyah dituduh berlaku curang dengan Tuah dan menjadi penyebab musibah yang menimpa adik lelaki kesayangannya. Aisyah benar-benar kecewa. Jebat mendustai cintanya. Dia dinikahi Jebat bukan untuk disayang, dicintai sepenuh hati tapi Jebat punya agendanya sendiri. Misi Jebat hanyalah satu, melunaskan dendamnya dan membalas balik segala kesengsaraan Tuah yang kononnya dikhianati Aisyah dahulu. Tuah sudah boleh menerima Aishah sebagai kakak iparnya, namun Jebat tetap cemburu melihat Tuah dan Aishah Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Azlee Khairi, Ikmal Amry, Mimi Ernida, Nina Fazurina, Wilma Muhammad dan Aznah Hamid.

Imran perlu berunding tentang perebutan kawasan dengan seorang lelaki misteri bernama Along.

programme.title: Pemburu Bayang
programme.desc: Zamri merupakan seorang bekas banduan yang ingin memulakan hidup baru bersama keluarganya. Namun, nasib tidak menyebelahinya apabila dia diburu kumpulan yang diketuai Ramon. Adik Zamri, Awie ialah seorang penyanyi kumpulan rock popular yang sedang menjalinkan hubungan cinta bersama Ella, yang juga penyanyi rock. Sesuatu terjadi yang menyebabkan Awie dan Ella putus hubungan. Manakala, Zamri pula diuji dengan pelbagai dugaan apabila isterinya dibunuh dengan kejam.

programme.title: Leftenan Adnan
programme.desc: Adnan memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang tentera dalam pasukan Askar Melayu setelah dikunjungi anggota tentera British yang datang ke kampungnya untuk merekrut lebih ramai anak tempatan. Tidak direstui keluarga, Adnan nekad untuk mengikuti latihan ketenteraan di Port Dickson. Perjuangan Leftenan Adnan dalam mempertahankan Tanah Melayu memberikan inspirasi kepada ramai anak muda tempatan.

programme.title: Ringgit Kasorrga
programme.desc: Kekayaan, kemewahan dan hawa nafsu - semuanya boleh didapati di Pulau Kasorrga. Pulau khas buat warga elit ini menjadi tempat buat orang kaya untuk mencari ketenangan dan kepuasan. Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Penyamun Tarbus
programme.desc: Tuan Said seorang yang kaya raya tetapi sering mengelat dari membayar cukai, menyimpan semua rekod di dalam peti besi miliknya. Malang sekali, rekod dan tarbus miliknya dicuri penyamun - untuk membalas dendam terhadap Tuan Said kerana tidak menerima mereka bekerja atas faktor umur. Tidak ingin rahsianya diketahui, diupahnya penyiasat penyendirian untuk menjejaki penyamun itu.

programme.title: Dia Ibuku
programme.desc: Rohani perlu bekerja keras untuk menyara anak-anaknya, Jamal dan Jamil kerana statusnya sebagai seorang janda. Tanah terpaksa digadai untuk membiayai pelajaran Jamal di luar negara, itulah kesanggupan Rohani demi anaknya. Jamal pun pulang membawa keluarga bakal isterinya selepas pulang ke tanah air. Perjumpaan itu membawa kembali kenangan silam yang pahit.

programme.title: Matinya Seorang Patriot
programme.desc: Pengerusi Melati Holdings, Haji Saaban meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba yang menimbulkan keraguan tentang kematiannya. Safuan mengesyaki bahawa kematian bapanya ada kena mengena dengan syarikat bapanya. Saiful yang pada mulanya ingin membalas dendam kematian bapanya mula berubah apabila jatuh cinta dengan anak kepada ahli lembaga pengarah. Safuan menganggap Saiful telah mengkhianati keluarga mereka.

Dia sering membantu membiayai pelajaran anak-anak Hamid dan menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi olehnya. Satu pertengkaran menyebabkan Hamid berhenti kerja namun Rahim tampil membantu mengambilnya bekerja di syarikat insurans miliknya.

Yazid pula keluar mencari Aisah di bandar - tetapi berdepan dengan pelbagai konflik dan tragedi.

programme.title: Aku Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Seorang petani dan anggota sukarelawan, Hamid dan Jaafar ingin menjatuhkan Jamali - wakil rakyat yang tidak telus dan kejam. Mereka berdua berusaha mendapatkan sokongan orang kampung supaya dapat menaikkan Hamid sebagai wakil rakyat baharu sekaligus menggantikan Jamali. programme.title: Ringgit Kasorrga
programme.desc: Kekayaan, kemewahan dan hawa nafsu - semuanya boleh didapati di Pulau Kasorrga. Pulau khas buat warga elit ini menjadi tempat buat orang kaya untuk mencari ketenangan dan kepuasan. Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Penyamun Tarbus
programme.desc: Tuan Said seorang yang kaya raya tetapi sering mengelat dari membayar cukai, menyimpan semua rekod di dalam peti besi miliknya. Malang sekali, rekod dan tarbus miliknya dicuri penyamun - untuk membalas dendam terhadap Tuan Said kerana tidak menerima mereka bekerja atas faktor umur. Tidak ingin rahsianya diketahui, diupahnya penyiasat penyendirian untuk menjejaki penyamun itu.

programme.title: Dia Ibuku
programme.desc: Rohani perlu bekerja keras untuk menyara anak-anaknya, Jamal dan Jamil kerana statusnya sebagai seorang janda. Perjumpaan itu membawa kembali kenangan silam yang pahit.

programme.title: Matinya Seorang Patriot
programme.desc: Pengerusi Melati Holdings, Haji Saaban meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba yang menimbulkan keraguan tentang kematiannya. Safuan mengesyaki bahawa kematian bapanya ada kena mengena dengan syarikat bapanya. Saiful yang pada mulanya ingin membalas dendam kematian bapanya mula berubah apabila jatuh cinta dengan anak kepada ahli lembaga pengarah. Safuan menganggap Saiful telah mengkhianati keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Jom Ke Sana Ep1
programme.desc: Setelah sekian lama berkerja di luar negara, Kally kembali ke Sarawak dan membuat keputusan untuk menerokai semula tempat menarik di Sarawak.Dia menghabiskan masa cutinya bersama kawan baiknya dengan cara "road trip" selama dia berada di Sarawak.

programme.title: Kek & Pastri Ep2
programme.desc: Seorang selebriti, menghasilkan resepi baharu untuk kek, pastri, dan hidangan savouri dengan menggunakan bahan-bahan tempatan dan teknik membakar dan mengukus untuk mencipta hidangan yang lazat & inovatif

programme.title: Remarkable Living S5 Ep2
programme.desc: From the trendy to traditional, radical to revolutionary, the new season of this award-winning series features inspiring stories around bespoke craftsmanship, gastronomy, artistry, architecture and spectacular spots - in South Korea, Thailand, Vietnam, France and Singapore.

programme.title: My Journey With Nature Ep6
programme.desc: Pengembaraan seorang wanita ke kawasan pendalaman yang belum diterokai diceritakan dalam "My Journey with Nature", yang menampilkan tarikan pelancongan alam semula jadi.

programme.title: (L) TVS Nightline
programme.desc: Memaparkan laporan peristiwa yang berlaku di seluruh Malaysia dalam bahasa English

programme.title: Staycation With Fattah S3 Ep11
programme.desc: Staycation With Fattah kembali lagi dengan Musim 3, menampilkan lebih banyak destinasi pelancongan menarik yang diterokai oleh Fattah di Sarawak, Negeri di Bawah Bayu Sabah, dan Semenanjung Malaysia.

programme.title: Hope Finds Love Ep7
programme.desc: Hope, sorang penulis muda yang hiper , sering gagal dalam cinta. Namun, jodohnya sentiasa dekat dimata.

programme.title: Rezeki Tanah Ep4
programme.desc: TVS mempersembahkan siri dokumentari Rezeki Tanah yang mengisahkan kecekalan 13 orang insan yang sanggup berkotor dan merisikokan diri untuk mencari rezeki, tidak kira daripada hasil hutan mahupun cucuk tanam demi kelangsungan hidup dan keluarga tercinta.

programme.title: Northland Of The Hornbills Ep6
programme.desc: North Land of the Hornbills highlights community-led efforts tackling poverty, education, healthcare, and the environment, showcasing unity, resilience, and hope in transforming lives and inspiring action.

programme.title: Kenyalang Rangers Ep1
programme.desc: Kenyalang Rangers adalah rancangan gameshow kanak-kanak berusia 12 tahun kebawah, yang akan disertai oleh 3 pasukan yang terdiri daripada 2 orang setiap pasukan dan dihoskan oleh Kenyalang Ranger.

programme.title: Arena Siber Ep12
programme.desc: Arena Siber mendedahkan keseimbangan bermain e-sukan dengan sihat serta cara menangani ketagihan. Dari pembangunan akar umbi, persediaan menggilap bakat, serta kisah kejayaan atlet.

programme.title: 3D Jobs Ep4
programme.desc: Aims to highlight and honor the unsung heroes of our communities who bravely perform challenging, hazardous, and dangerous jobs, showcasing their daily lives and their life stories beyond their work.

programme.title: Peluang Ketiga
programme.desc: Zulaikha dan Yusuf telah menjalinkan hubungan sejak zaman universiti lagi. Namun, hubungan mereka terputus apabila Yusuf tidak bersetuju dengan keputusan Zulaikha untuk menjadi seorang penyanyi. Zulaikha kemudian bertemu dengan Mikhail, seorang lelaki berhati mulia yang sentiasa menyokong segala impiannya. Sementara itu, Yusuf meneruskan kerjayanya sebagai pelumba basikal profesional dan jatuh cinta dengan seorang wartawan sukan bernama Alya.Namun, apabila Mikhail melamar Zulaikha, hati Yusuf mula dilanda cemburu. Mampukah Yusuf melupakan Zulaikha dan menerima hakikat bahawa cinta mereka mungkin sudah berlalu?

programme.title: Dunia Baru The Movie
programme.desc: Filem ini bermula apabila Opie menemui sepucuk surat daripada Anizah yang menyatakan bahawa dia ingin berkahwin dengan teman lelakinya, Fazley, dan telah menguburkan impiannya untuk menyambung pelajaran ke UK.

programme.title: Kaki Kitai
programme.desc: Din AKA Drango dan Ayoi adalah dua sahabat yang juga merupakan penipu. Mereka berdua datang ke Kuala Lumpur dan secara tidak sengaja bertemu semula dengan seorang kawan lama yang kini bekerja sebagai pegawai polis. Namun, hidup mereka mula berubah apabila mereka menemui sebuah beg sampah yang dipenuhi dengan wang tunai, yang kemudian mereka gunakan untuk membayar hutang.

programme.title: Abang Lejen
programme.desc: Dua beradik yang kehilangan ibu bapa mereka sejak kecil. Si abang sanggup mempertaruhkan nyawanya demi melindungi adiknya walau apa pun yang terjadi.

programme.title: Sejoli
programme.desc: Jo (Bront Palarae) dan Gina (Maya Karin) sedang menyembuhkan hati yang terluka di Phuket apabila takdir mempertemukan mereka. Pada mulanya mereka saling membenci, tetapi apabila mereka mendapat tahu bahawa bekas kekasih masing-masing, Hardy (Remy Ishak) dan Nita (Izara Aishah), akan berkahwin, mereka merancang untuk menggagalkan majlis perkahwinan tersebut.

programme.title: 1 Lawan Satu
programme.desc: Saleh dan Radhi, dua 'pejuang' yang datang dari latar belakang berbeza, namun bertemu di gelanggang pertarungan. Saleh dibesarkan dengan kemahiran seni mempertahankan diri dan kini sedang mencari adiknya yang telah hilang. Radhi pula bertarung demi menyelamatkan adik perempuannya, Sara, yang sedang sakit tenat dan memerlukan RM50,000 untuk rawatan.

programme.title: Cincin Pusaka
programme.desc: Alina dan Sofian adalah dua beradik yang saling cemburu, berlumba mengalahkan satu sama lain sejak kecil. Setelah kematian nenek, mereka berebut untuk memiliki cincin pusaka nenek yang kononnya mempunyai magis tertentu. Tetapi pelbagai halangan terjadi untuk mereka mewarisinya. Mampukah mereka menghadapi segala rintangan demi sebentuk cincin pusaka?

programme.title: Nana Dan Jam Atok
programme.desc: Kisah tentang Nana dikenali sebagai seorang pelajar yang pemalas dan sering lewat ke sekolah. Alasan yang sering digunakan adalah jam di rumahnya rosak dan tidak berbunyi. Puas ayahnya menukar jam dibilik Nana dengan harapan ada perubahan.

programme.title: Ruang Temu S1 Ep55
programme.desc: Program temu bual bersama Tony Eusoff yang mengupas pengalaman peribadi beliau berkaitan pengalaman beliau di dalam industri seni

programme.title: Aji Noh Motor
programme.desc: Aji ialah seorang abang yang sangat mengambil berat dan sanggup melakukan apa sahaja untuk adiknya, Noh. Noh, seorang yang berpegang kepada ajaran Islam, berasa tidak senang dengan tabiat Aji yang suka berlumba haram. Noh dilahirkan buta dan menjalani kehidupannya dengan melakukan perkara-perkara yang berfaedah, manakala abangnya pula gemar menyertai perlumbaan haram dan melepak bersama rakan-rakannya. Walaupun Aji mempunyai perangai yang tidak baik, dia sangat menyayangi Noh. Dia sanggup memenuhi permintaan Noh walaupun permintaan itu mustahil untuk dicapai. Semuanya bermula pada hari lahir Noh apabila dia menyatakan hasrat untuk menunaikan haji. Aji yang tidak mampu untuk menunaikan permintaan tersebut telah berusaha mengumpul wang demi merealisasikan impian adiknya. Walaupun terpaksa melakukan perkara yang haram dan bertentangan dengan agama.

programme.title: Syawal Mencari Cinta
programme.desc: Pada pagi Raya, Syawal melepak bersama rakannya dan mereka tidak menunaikan solat sunat Hari Raya. Setelah selesai solat sunat Hari Raya, dia ternampak seorang gadis yang tidak pernah dilihatnya di kampung sebelum ini. Syawal terus berkesimpulan bahawa dia telah menemui cinta sejati. Dia telah mengunjung setiap rumah di kampung untuk menjejaki gadis tersebut. Selepas sekian lama mencari tanpa membuahkan hasil, Syawal terus mengumumkan kepada seluruh kampung bahawa dia akan melaksanakan rumah terbuka untuk hari raya dan semua orang dijemput hadir ke rumahnya. Namun demikian, setelah selesai rumah terbukanya, gadis yang dicari-cari Syawal masih tidak kelihatan. Dia kecewa lalu berputus asa. Tanpa sedar, gadis yang dijejaki selama ini adalah Cinta, sepupunya sendiri.

programme.title: Reaksiar S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan perkongsian pengalaman dan reaksi artis-artis jemputan setelah melihat kembali klip-klip lakonan mereka.

programme.title: Gerabak Cinta
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luna, usahawan berjaya yang ditipu tunangnya, Razi. Dia kecewa apabila perniagaan yang mereka usahakan rugi kerana Razi terbabit dengan skandal wang serta mempunyai perempuan simpanan. Sementara itu, Gie pula baru saja dibuang kerja. Walaupun masih mencari kerja, dia sangat tenang dan tetap ceria. Gie reda dengan situasi menimpanya.

programme.title: Jodoh Tak Salah Alamat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luqman pernah mengenali seorang gadis bernama Diana ketika Diana melanggar keretanya dahulu. Diana berpenampilan seksi dan mengamalkan cara hidup barat membuatkan Luqman bersangka buruk terhadap Diana. Satu hari, Luqman ke masjid dan terserempak dengan seorang gadis cantik iaitu Adawiyah. Tanpa mengetahui, Adawiyah dan Diana adalah orang yang sama. Diana pernah terlibat dengan kemalangan dan sejak itu hidupnya berubah sepenuhnya.

programme.title: Tukul Arwana One Man Show Ep23
programme.desc: Sebuah program bual bicara yang dihoskan Tukul Arwana di Indosiar menyajikan hiburan terbaru yang akan menemani penonton semasa pandemik COVID-19 bersama bintang jemputan, tokoh masyarakat dan mereka yang tular di media sosial.

programme.title: Lensa Lokal Medan Ep6
programme.desc: Lensa Lokal Medan merupakan sebuah dokumentari yang menyelami kehidupan masyarakat tempatan serta keunikan budaya di Medan.

programme.title: Tobatnya Lelaki Egois Yang Mengubah Takdirnya
programme.desc: Kerana ulah Danang, sang ayah meninggal dunia. Perasaan penyesalan menyelubungi Danang. Sejak itu, Danang berubah menjadi anak yang soleh dan membantu ibunya untuk memenuhi keperluan hidup mereka.

programme.title: Superstar Junior S2 Ep4
programme.desc: Superstar Junior S2 kembali mengetengahkan bakat asli kanak-kanak tempatan yang luar biasa dan menghiburkan, sesuai untuk tontonan seisi keluarga. Dengan persembahan yang comel, penuh tenaga dan menyentuh hati, rancangan ini bukan sahaja mempamerkan kehebatan generasi muda, malah turut diserikan dengan penglibatan juri dan mentor popular.

programme.title: Doyan Makan Ep14
programme.desc: Doyan Makan menjemput penonton untuk mengikuti perjalanan dan pengalaman kulinari untuk makanan popular di kawasan tersebut, serta akan meninjau informasi tentang tempat, harga dan proses penghasilan makanan yang mereka nikmati.

programme.title: My Heart Ep41
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. Di sana, dia bertemu Mike, seorang pelakon drama popular yang sebenarnya berperwatakan sensitif dan bermasalah, berbeza dengan wataknya di kaca TV. Perkenalan mereka secara kebetulan menjadi semakin rapat apabila mereka mula mengenali diri sebenar masing-masing. Namun, cinta mereka diuji apabila terbongkar bahawa ibu Mike, Rika, adalah isteri kedua kepada ayah Raisa, menyebabkan perebutan harta antara keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Lepoq Keq Tanjung Selor Ep38

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa Ep295
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan Ep5180
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protg Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Rus financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the clients data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Fight Back to School II
programme.desc: Star Chow (Stephen Chow) is an officer in the Royal Hong Kong Police's elite Special Duties Unit (SDU). During a meeting with his senior officer, Inspector Yip (Deanie Ip), Star jokingly suggests he wish to be reassigned to the traffic unit. Star immediately finds himself demoted to Constable engaging in traffic duty on the streets of Hong Kong. After being made the scapegoat for a failed high school terrorist investigation, Star hastily resigns from the police. He decides to enroll at the high school to launch his own private investigation. But Star realises the investigation won't be easy when he discovers that the bumbling, incompetent CID detective Tat (Ng Man Tat) is also undercover at the high school.

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quins trust, Nick becomes his protg and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: Shining for One Thing
programme.desc: Zhang Wan Sen plans to confess his crush on Lin Bei Xing after the college entrance exam, but an accident changes everything tragically. As Zhang feels helpless and devastated, he fortuitously travels back in time with Lin before the accident happens. Can he make amends and convey his regrets this time?

programme.title: Panda Plan
programme.desc: After legendary kung fu star Jackie Chan adopts the panda Hu Hu, an international crime syndicate places a massive bounty on the bear. Joined by his agent and Hu Hus caretaker, Jackie embarks on a daring quest to outsmart the villains.

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness

programme.title: The Phantom Lover
programme.desc: In 1926 China, Sung, a talented singer, is deeply in love with To, a sweet innocent girl from a wealthy family. Their love evokes strong disapproval from To's father and bitter jealousy from her designated fianc, a young man chosen by her family. This is a story about a singer and a wealthy girl battling to be together in a traditional community.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: The Ex-Files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixs (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: The Exodus
programme.desc: A low-ranking cop discovers a group of women, including his superior, Madam Fang and his wife, plotting to eliminate the world of men.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighbouring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: The Wig
programme.desc: Meng Zhong is a law graduate overwhelmed by despair after failing the bar exam three times and vents his frustration on a drunken passenger one stormy night. Twenty years later, Meng is a successful lawyer, but his investigation into a sexual assault case involving a young girl rekindles haunting memories he cannot escape.

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling, a pregnant painter, moves into her dream home after winning an award and hires a confinement nanny. As she begins her one-month confinement after giving birth to her daughter, inexplicable incidents start happening in the house, threatening both her and her baby

programme.title: All U Need is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Three bizarre tales intertwine in this horror satire set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: Ha Ha Ha Happy New Year!!
programme.desc: Business tycoon Duan is kidnapped and seriously injured by the "Shadow Empire", accidentally losing his memory. Duan is looked after by Su, a temple owner, and as he slowly recovers, Duan discovers that he has been replaced by a doppelgnger, prompting him to uncover a shocking hidden secret.

programme.title: From Vegas to Macau III
programme.desc: Ken holds a wedding ceremony in Macau for his daughter Rainbow. However, an explosion during the wedding causes Rainbow to fall into coma, while Ken and his friend Mark, are accused of engulfing some illicit money. Enraged, Ken swears to seek vengeance and pursue the mastermind who has gotten them involved in his evil plan.

programme.title: Table for Six
programme.desc: In this comedy, three brothers reside in a home inherited from their late parents. The eldest brother insists they have dinner at home every night as a family, but tensions begin to rise when their girlfriends join in as well. Love, friendship, jealousy and complicated relationships are all on the menu for this table for six!

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong 2013
programme.desc: Sung Chi Hung and Ha Shek Lam worked at a Chinese restaurant when they were young and both fell in love with the owners daughter, Yeung. Sung and Yeung eventually got married and took over the restaurant. Many years later, Sung meets Ha who is now a real estate tycoon and plans to buy out the restaurant. Can Sung save the restaurant?

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: One of the great Kung-fu film characters is Beggar Su, a legendary Ching Dynasty figure who was also a member of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers. Little-known director Liu Shih-yu uses the best Kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer to tell a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure, as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liang's work, but essentially an image to him as well.

programme.title: Mad Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Master Chen was an esteemed Monkey Kung Fu master, until he is framed and crippled by a ruthless villain and ends up becoming a wandering artiste. When Chen meets a young man, Little Monkey, on the streets, he decides to teach him all his monkey kung fu moves. Both men eventually team up to avenge Chen's past insult.

programme.title: Come Drink With Me
programme.desc: The brother of the mystery swordswoman "Golden Swallow is kidnapped. She joins forces with a beggar Drunken Cat who is skilled in martial arts to free her brother from a Buddhist monastery run by a corrupt abbot. The film was selected as Hong Kong's entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 39th Academy Awards.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brother's death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: Murderer Pursues
programme.desc: Wang Chung was a valued actor long before he became a director, but as a filmmaker, he helped create some of the most interesting thrillers Shaw Brothers ever released - including this fascinating crime saga of a Sino-Vietnamese crime gang. Danny Lee stars as a misunderstood refugee while Ray Lui plays a cop struggling against his own conscience to ensure that justice is upheld.

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: Rivals Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: As Shen and Wong Fei Hung's relationship turns sour, Shen frames Wong and his disciple for murder. They are saved by a businessman Zhou, but Wong must win the Lion Dance Trophy to return Zhou's favour. Can Wong Fei Hung defeat all skilled martial artists and complete his mission?

programme.title: The Bride From Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: The Anonymous Heroes
programme.desc: In this action comedy, two young men join a rebel group after the Chinese Revolution of 1911 and accidentally become patriotic heroes. Assisted by a warlord's daughter, they successfully help the rebels steal weapons from the warlord.

programme.title: The Tiger And The Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium house's owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: Clans Of Intrigue
programme.desc: Heroic outlaw Chu Liu Xiang is dining with his friend Monk Wu Hua, when Gong from the Holy Water Palace appears and accuses Chu of stealing the holy water from her Palace and using it for various murders. Chu denies, and is given a month to find the murderer or be killed by Gong. To prove his innocence, Chu decides to investigate the case

programme.title: My Name Ain'T Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: My Rebellious Son
programme.desc: A corrupt official attempts to steal a priceless Buddha statue from a temple to please a group of Westerners. Luckily, Doctor Zhang and his son manage to defeat the Western boxers, the Japanese Kendo opponents and the Western longsword fighters with Chinese kung fu, thus saving the Buddha statue.

programme.title: Sex, Love And Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: A Deadly Secret
programme.desc: A corrupt magistrate, obsessed with finding a hidden treasure, jails and tortures his daughter's lover and buries his daughter alive! Ironically, it is in her coffin that the secret to the hidden treasure is found, setting off a frenzy of destruction.

programme.title: Let'S Fall In Love
programme.desc: Da Yung, the son of a rich entrepreneur, meets Lian Lian, the niece of a kindergarten principal by chance. They fall into a misunderstanding on the first meeting, causing Da Yung to lose his wallet. Further misunderstanding occurs when he tries to get her to act as his fianc so as to drive away two women whom he does not like

programme.title: Forbidden Tales Of Two Cities
programme.desc: Li Han-hsiang wrote and directed this charming and fascinating comedy, Forbidden Tales Of Two Cities. The two cities in the picture are Macau, where a love quartet is a morally-unsound source for sexual entertainment; and Hong Kong, where a woman enters a gambler's apartment to find four shackles hanging from his ceiling to aid in kinky activities.

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Bao's chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: The Jade Raksha
programme.desc: A fearsome swordswoman known as The Jade Raksha appears in the martial arts world and begins killing people whose surname is Yan. A swordsman figures out who she is and asks her why. Apparently a Yan killed her family 18 years ago and she only has vengeance on her mind

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Long's wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: The Eight Diagram Pole Fighter
programme.desc: The Yang Generals were ambushed by the enemies and only two of the sons survived. The fifth son of Yang's escapes to Shaolin temple and learns the pole-fighting techniques from the monks, eventually creating his own Eight Diagram Pole Fight and teaming up with the Shaolin monks to avenge his family.

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: Lady Of The Law
programme.desc: Chan, the chief of Wan Sheng Escort, is forced to raise his opponent's son, Yim. While Chan forbids Yim to practice martial arts, Yim secretly learns it. Ten years later, a rapist appears and Yim is arrested by a lady constable as the suspect. The rapist turns out to be Chan's elder son and Yim is framed by the Chans. Can Yim prove his innocence?

programme.title: The Love Eterne
programme.desc: Ying Tai disguises herself as a boy to go to school and falls hopelessly in love with her classmate, Shan Bo. After Shan Bo realizes her true identity, he proposes marriage to Ying Tai. However, they are kept apart as she is engaged to another man. Knowing Shan Bo died in despair, Ying Tai is in deep sorrow and kills herself at his grave.

programme.title: Ambitious Kung Fu Girl
programme.desc: The lovely Michelle Mei Suet plays a spoiled girl Szu-szu who ignores her true love Yang Fan to go off in search of a swordsman Chin Ko she idolizes. The search sets off one great action scene after another, until she's threatened to be sold into slavery but Yang Fan arrives in the nick of time! This amusing and entertaining variation on the standard kung-fu film is definitely a winner.

programme.title: Beyond The Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Hun's warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: One-Armed Swordsman
